tags: I feel really terrible to make this post
And I'm sorry for sharing my personal story with you you guys didn't need to know it aah
title: HELP ; ;
body:
Okay, uh, my tablet wacom kinda broke on me right now, I can’t use it anymore and I can’t afford to buy a new one or to fix it since we got kicked out of our house by my father and he’s been stealing our very few finances. I’m trying to find a job, but I have some legal shit to take care of first and it can take a while.
So uh, if you have some spare money, please consider help a queer boy out? Drawing is my only occupation and way to earn money at the moment, without my tablet, I really can’t do shit. I feel already awful to make this post. 

A tablet would cost me around 130€ (150$)! If you can’t donate, it’s all good, but I’ll be really grateful if you could reblog so people can see it!

You can donate with ko-fi or paypal!

(In case you’re curious about my art, you can find some here and here!)
